{"tid":1351554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝身] 大家有無穿皮帶既習慣","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:24:39.000Z","uid":2998,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4554f34a32aad8c4c1eeaf49a2acac396da238","tid":1351554,"uid":2998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"Ladies and Gentlemen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個著衫企理, 有fashion sense既人<br />\n出門口著褲著裙都穿返條皮帶係好合理既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶扣硬班班, 比佢扑中都真係暈得一陣陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶身柔情似水, 一鞭鞭留下愛的烙印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n穿起頸到仲可以當頸巾, 緊緊勒出一絲絲暖意令你抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎種一定基本款喇, 大鋼扣皮身, 襯衫容易<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.uniqlo.com.hk/hmall/test/u0000000000960/main/first/561/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uniqlo.com.hk%2Fhmall%2Ftest%2Fu0000000000960%2Fmain%2Ffirst%2F561%2F1.jpg&h=dd212cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uniqlo.com.hk/pc/zh_HK/product-detail.html?productCode=u0000000000960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uniqlo.com.hk%2Fpc%2Fzh_HK%2Fproduct-detail.html%3FproductCode%3Du0000000000960&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn24Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e544c7a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uniqlo.com.hk/pc/zh_HK/product-detail.html?productCode=u0000000000960</a><br />\n<br />\n筆直少既可以攬黎d款, 鋼頭布身皮尾, 輕身高效平價, 性價比高<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1656455/k$1ae694b67b32db93f9d018b4f81a8ad7/sq/.webp?f=1000x1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1656455%2Fk%241ae694b67b32db93f9d018b4f81a8ad7%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D1000x1000&h=e760cb31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-s1/_/R-p-172138?[img]mc=8547499&amp;c=%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fp%2F500-s1%2F_%2FR-p-172138%3F%5Bimg%5Dmc%3D8547499%26c%3D%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%2589%25B2%5B%2Furl%5D&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn24Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b2f4e5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-s1/_/R-p-172138?[img]mc=8547499&amp;c=%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n黎隻就好比較岩文青斯文巴絲, 全鋼頭加皮身, 一睇就知你pro<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.zara.net/photos///2019/I/0/2/p/5919/304/800/2/w/1024/5919304800_1_1_1.jpg?ts=1561724381807\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.zara.net%2Fphotos%2F%2F%2F2019%2FI%2F0%2F2%2Fp%2F5919%2F304%2F800%2F2%2Fw%2F1024%2F5919304800_1_1_1.jpg%3Fts%3D1561724381807&h=4d13906b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zara.com/hk/zt/%E9%9B%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%AE%E8%85%B0%E5%B8%B6-p05919304.html?v1=21495548&amp;v2=1283049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zara.com%2Fhk%2Fzt%2F%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259A%25AE%25E8%2585%25B0%25E5%25B8%25B6-p05919304.html%3Fv1%3D21495548%26v2%3D1283049&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn24Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ffc36f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zara.com/hk/zt/%E9%9B%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%AE%E8%85%B0%E5%B8%B6-p05919304.html?v1=21495548&amp;v2=1283049</a>"},{"pid":"bcd1f9c0923a1b2681cd5642409e2702d13d3f47","tid":1351554,"uid":2998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"屌開錯台, 算喇唔搬返潮流台喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeefc695112c094421c8455d156c76f1ebe9d225","tid":1351554,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2674cb97f710f264f012fe6c78a6ed76c419db1d","tid":1351554,"uid":7409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep